Tyrael needed a report of his troops. He sent a message on Tripred 
frequencies.

Tyrael: All troops, report your status. Deathstar and Dreadplague, 
confirm the progression of your objectives, but stay there. 
Darkangel, confirm the status of the battle. Is it finished?

Dreadplague did not wait very long before replying.

Dreadplague: I'm still waiting for Hydras to give me a slave. He's 
recalling his troops, though this could be bad for us, if he stands 
ready to grab the gun to himself.

Tyrael chuckled lightly.

Tyrael: I understand your concern, Daughter, but I found a way to 
address it. I will show you later.
